Name: Call of Juarez: Bound in Blood

Achievements.Name: Arkansas Fried Rooster
Achievements.Description: Blow up 10 chickens with dynamite.

Achievements.Name: Magnificent Thirteen
Achievements.Description: Unlock all classes (ranked only).

Achievements.Name: High Noon
Achievements.Description: Kill 4 enemies between 12:00 p.m. and 12:15 p.m. (local time, ranked play counts).

Achievements.Name: Well Invested
Achievements.Description: Buy 20 second level and 10 third level upgrades (ranked only).

Achievements.Name: Drive-By
Achievements.Description: Kill a total of 5 enemies while horseback (ranked play counts).

Achievements.Name: Unforgiven
Achievements.Description: Kill 10 enemies as an invincible wanted (ranked only).

Achievements.Name: Welcome to the Frontier
Achievements.Description: Finish a full Wild West Legends game (ranked only).

Achievements.Name: Crime Does Pay
Achievements.Description: Win 5 rounds as an Outlaw (ranked only).

Achievements.Name: Tin Star
Achievements.Description: Win 5 rounds as a Lawman (ranked only).

Achievements.Name: Been There, Done That
Achievements.Description: Play a full Wild West Legends game on every level (both match and revenge match count; ranked only).

Achievements.Name: 99 Scalps
Achievements.Description: Deliver 99 headshots (ranked play counts).

Achievements.Name: Jack of All Trades
Achievements.Description: Play a full game with each class (ranked only).

Achievements.Name: Goldrush!
Achievements.Description: Collect a total of $1 000 000 (ranked play counts) to unlock golden weapons in multiplayer.

Achievements.Name: Crowbait
Achievements.Description: Finish the game on at least easy difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Between Hay and Grass
Achievements.Description: Finish the game on at least medium difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Curly Wolf
Achievements.Description: Finish the game on hard difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Act I
Achievements.Description: Complete Act I.

Achievements.Name: Act II
Achievements.Description: Complete Act II.

Achievements.Name: Act III
Achievements.Description: Complete Act III.

Achievements.Name: Act IV
Achievements.Description: Complete Act IV.

Achievements.Name: Ray's Story
Achievements.Description: Finish every chapter playing as Ray.

Achievements.Name: Thomas' Story
Achievements.Description: Finish every chapter playing as Thomas.

Achievements.Name: D-Day
Achievements.Description: On chapter I, destroy all rafts before they land.

Achievements.Name: Mayhem
Achievements.Description: On chapter III, kill 20 armed enemies while riding the stagecoach.

Achievements.Name: Quite a Ride
Achievements.Description: On chapter IX, on the lift, destroy everything that is thrown at you.

Achievements.Name: Man of the Hood
Achievements.Description: On chapter XII, playing as Thomas, use only bow throughout the whole level.

Achievements.Name: Gotta Catch'em All
Achievements.Description: Collect all secrets.

Achievements.Name: Boy Scout
Achievements.Description: Finish one side quest.

Achievements.Name: Shield of Hope
Achievements.Description: Finish all side quests.

Achievements.Name: Quick Hands
Achievements.Description: Kill 7 people during one concentration mode.

Achievements.Name: Frag Steal
Achievements.Description: Kill all enemies in a single Cooperative Concentration Mode.

Achievements.Name: Untouchable
Achievements.Description: Finish any chapter, except for VI and VIII, without getting severely wounded.

Achievements.Name: Fireworks
Achievements.Description: Shoot 2 enemy dynamite sticks in mid air.

Achievements.Name: None Shall Hide
Achievements.Description: Shoot an enemy through a wall.

Achievements.Name: Mad Carpenter
Achievements.Description: Kill 5 enemies with a chair.

Achievements.Name: Pistol Expert
Achievements.Description: Kill 250 People using pistols (ranked play counts).

Achievements.Name: Rifle Expert
Achievements.Description: Kill 250 People using rifles (ranked play counts).

Achievements.Name: Shotgun Expert
Achievements.Description: Kill 250 People using shotguns (ranked play counts).

Achievements.Name: Forgiveth Me, Lord
Achievements.Description: Kill 2000 enemies (ranked play counts).

Achievements.Name: Rowing-Race Cheater
Achievements.Description: On chapter XI, kill all the Indians during canoe chase.

Achievements.Name: Sharpshooter Distraction
Achievements.Description: On chapter IV, playing as Ray, kill sharpshooters without Thomas' help.

Achievements.Name: Sharpshooter Destruction
Achievements.Description: On chapter IV, playing as Thomas, kill sharpshooters in 10 seconds.

Achievements.Name: Catcher in the Rye
Achievements.Description: On chapter II, in the field, kill enemy soldiers using knives without being detected.

Achievements.Name: Yankee Cow
Achievements.Description: On chapter II, don't kill the cow.

Achievements.Name: Vindicator
Achievements.Description: Kill a total of 30 enemies with movable gatling.

Achievements.Name: On the Right Track
Achievements.Description: Collect a total of $200 000 (ranked play counts) to unlock silver weapons in multiplayer.

Achievements.Name: Old West Legend
Achievements.Description: Finish the game on very hard difficulty.
